channel.title: Jeep Modification Manual!
channel.description:
Check out this awesome Jeep Manual made by students on our FIRST Robotics Team! We just held a Community Build and Hackathon where 7 of these jeeps were built. They worked great and they have a handy remote. I'll put pictures and links to videos on the Build Showcase a little later, but thought I would post the manual. Please feel free to provide feedback!
Special thanks to students: Aiden Jacobs, George Whitehill, and Aasim Hawa for putting this together.
You can find the manual at the link below! https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ymEICkTm1QsL1RXihIAa8IOeIK-LPxAg/view?usp=sharing
